Package: synbreed
Type: Package
Title: Collection of methods developed for the synbreed project for synergistic plant and animal breeding
Version: 0.2-1
Date: 2010-30-06
Author: Valentin Wimmer
Depends: RColorBrewer, lattice, igraph, MASS, LDheatmap
Suggests: kinship
Maintainer: Valentin Wimmer <Valentin.Wimmer@wzw.tum.de>                                                 
Description: A package containing tools for plant and animal breeding. All steps of an analysis pipeline for genomic selection are part of this package: Methods for coding marker data, functions to set up pedigree and compute relationship matrices based on marker data or based on pedigree. 
URL: http://synbreed.r-forge.r-project.org/
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: no
ZipData: no